The paper discusses a reinforcement learning algorithm for solving Markov Decision Process problems. This falls under the broad category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also mentions the optimization of energy efficient data transmission and management of queues, which are topics covered by cs.DS and cs.SY. Finally, the paper discusses convergence speed and computational complexity, which are topics covered by cs.MA.
